data.description: You will fall in love with this stunning brick home near the golf course, 35W, Tanger Outlet Mall, Alliance Town Center & TMS! Located in NWISD this lovely home features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bath, fresh interior paint, new fixtures and LVP were updated in 2023. The large covered brick front porch welcomes guests right away. The interior is bright with an easy floor-plan for a growing family. The front room off the entry can be a dining room, home office or 2nd living area. The owners suite is located on the first floor, the other 3 bedrooms are upstairs with a loft! The open kitchen features stainless steal appliances with a gas stove, granite counters with an updated overlay and eat in kitchen. If you love to golf, shop or you love the raceway life the location has so much to offer!
